io.spire.api
Class Session

java.lang.Object
  io.spire.api.Resource
      io.spire.api.Session

public class Session
extends Resource

A session object gives you access to privileged resources. The resources attribute will provide a list of them, by name. For example, you'll have a resource called channels, which will give you a list of channel resources.

Since:
1.0
